  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>\"Jinkies\"</em></p><h5 id=\"benefit\">Benefit</h5><p>When you are wearing glasses, you add a d4 to all investigation and insight checks. Additionally, once per session, while you are involved in a social encounter where two or more parties are in conflict, you may raise your glasses, and reveal a new piece of information (this piece of information does not need to be true). <br />When you do this, you gain advantage on your next persuasion or deception check.</p><h5 id=\"negative\">Negative</h5><p>When you are not wearing glasses, you gain the blinded condition.</p>",
